root: ^I've been cooking up a storm to make the best possible story to pitch to you. I'll be waiting.

^It was an ordinary day at the pizza joint. Not a single worry in the world for Kean Cooke, an all-star pizza chef at the local Domino’s. His humble life changed forever when the alluring, steadfast Dominique Driscoll walked into his workplace. In this seductive thriller, watch over the pair in this risque relationship.between Kean and Dom as they navigate a new type of love– but don’t forget your safeword.
